      <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#CB6CE6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span>Reducción de riesgo tecnológico</div>
      <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#CB6CE6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span>Equipo dedicado sin costo de contratación interna</div>
      <div class="benefit"><span class="benefit-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#CB6CE6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span>Precio según alcance — bajo consulta</div>
